agher\n| con1 = Billy Ghent, [[Arthur Singe]]\n| pen1 =\n| try2 = Wareing, Unknown x 1\n| con2 =\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Carlaw Park 2\n| attendance = 4000\n| referee = W Mincham\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 22 April\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Devonport\n| score = 17\u201332\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Opening of the Season/Standard of Play Moderate\n| page =9\n| work=[[The New Zealand Herald]]| volume=LIX| issue=18073\n| date = 1922-04-24\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19220424.2.107.1\n| accessdate = 2019-08-26}}</ref>| away = City\n| try1 = Johnston, Harry Douglas, [[Neville St George]] 2, Scott\n| con1 =\n| pen1 = [[Neville St George]]\n| try2 = [[Bert Laing]], [[Bill Davidson (rugby league)|Bill Davidson]] 2, Jack Keenan, [[Alf Townsend]], [[George Paki]], Unknown x 1\n| con2 = [[Bert Laing]], [[Bill Davidson (rugby league)|Bill Davidson]] 3\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Devonport Domain\n| attendance =\n| referee = Archie Ferguson\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 22 April\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Richmond\n| score = 2\u201314\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Opening of the Season/Standard of Play Moderate\n| page =9\n| work=[[The New Zealand Herald]]| volume=LIX| issue=18073\n| date = 1922-04-24\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19220424.2.107.1\n| accessdate = 2019-08-26}}</ref>\n| away = Athletic\n| try1 =\n| con1 =\n| pen1 = Henderson\n| try2 = [[Eric Grey]] 2, Hall, G Yardley\n| con2 = G Yardley\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Grey Lynn Park\n| attendance =\n| referee = T Neill\n}}\n\n===Round 2===\nIn the match between Athletic and Ponsonby [[Eric Grey]] had a highly unusual collection of points after he scored a try, and kicked a conversion, a penalty, a goal from a mark, and a drop goal.\n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 29 April\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Athletic\n| score = 23\u20135\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Athletics Defeat Ponsonby\n| page =7\n| work=[[The New Zealand Heral